ama Kiss Shojo Anime's Trailer Previews English Dub|website=Anime News Network|accessdate=Jul 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Karneval (manga)|Karneval]]'' || Min\u00e9 || Ep. 1 || <ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2014/04/01/karneval-english-cast-announcement/ | title=Karneval English Cast Announcement | publisher=Funimation | work=Funimation Blog | date=April 1, 2014 | accessdate=December 7, 2015 | last=Lee | first=Michelle}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Hetalia: Axis Powers|Hetalia: The Beautiful World]]'' || Female Prussia (Nyotalia), Main Protagonist's Wife || || <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-05-12/funimation-announces-cast-for-gender-bending-hetalia-ova|title=Funimation Announces Cast for Gender-Bending Hetalia OVA|website=Anime News Network|accessdate=Jul 5, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Death Parade]]'' ||  Quin || || <ref>{{cite web|title=Funimation Announces Death Parade English Dub Cast|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2015-02-17/funimation-announces-death-parade-english-dub-cast/.85107|publisher=Anime News Network|accessdate=17 February 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Assassination Classroom]]'' || Mary Anne Cooper || Ep. 10 || <ref>{{cite episode | time=Closing credits | title=L and R Time | work=Funimation | episode=List of Assassination Classroom episodes #Assassination Classroom (2015)| series=Assassination Classroom | serieslink=Assassination Classroom | number=10 | year=2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Ben-To]]'' || Kyo Sawagi<!-- Vice President --> || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-04-19/funimation-unveils-ben-to-english-dub-cast-trailer|title=Funimation Unveils Ben-To's English Dub Cast, Trailer|publisher=Anime News Network|accessdate=April 19, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Nobunagun]]'' || Mary || Ep. 13 || <ref>{{cite episode | at=Closing credits | title=Nobunagun | work=Funimation | episode=Nobunagun #Anime | series=Nobunagun | serieslink=Nobunagun 