e Arc]]'' || Monomi || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2016/07/28/danganronpa-3-the-end-of-hopes-peak-high-school-broadcast-dub-cast-announcement/|title=Danganronpa 3: The End of Hope's Peak High School Broadcast Dub Cast Announcement|publisher=[[Funimation]].com|date=July 28, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016\u2013present || ''[[Fairy Tail]]'' || Minerva Orland || ||\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[The Disastrous Life of Saiki K.]]'' || Kaido's Mother || Eps. 10, 12 || <ref>{{cite tweet|user=soymilkpudding|author=Ayu|number=785874311663857668|date=11 October 2016|title=@Unknownsage Kaidou's mom is Anastasia Munoz and Pussy is voiced by @DawnMBennettVA.}}?p=v</ref>\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Garo: The Animation]]'' || Anna Lu\u00eds || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.funimation.com/blog/2016/02/27/garo-the-animation-english-voice-cast-announcement/|title=GARO THE ANIMATION \u2013 English Voice Cast Announcement!|publisher=[[Funimation]]|date=February 27, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Keijo!!!!!!!!]]'' || Kyoko Shirayuki || credited as Staci Moon ||<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218220345/https://www.funimation.com/blog/2016/10/18/fall-2016-simuldub-english-cast-announcements-for-the-love-of-dubs/|title=Fall 2016 SimulDub\u2122 English Cast Announcements \u2013 For The Love of Dubs - Funimation - Blog!|date=2017-02-18|website=web.archive.org|access-date=2019-07-06}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Overlord (novel series)|Overlord]]'' || Narberal Gamma || || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2016-08-12/funimation-reveals-dub-casts-for-overlord-shimoneta-1st-live-action-rurouni-kenshin-film-6th-hetalia-season/.105328|title=Funimation Reveals Dub Casts For Overlord, Shimoneta, 1st Live-Action Rurouni Kenshin Film, 6th Hetalia Season|publisher=Anime News Network|accessdate=August 12, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Puzzle & Dragons#Anime|Puzzle & Dragons X]]'' || Valkyrie || ||<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.funimation.com/blog/2017/01/0